StoredProcedureOraclev10g.name: CREATE_ACCOUNT_WITH_DATES
StoredProcedureOraclev10g.source:
CREATE OR REPLACE procedure WVC.CREATE_ACCOUNT_WITH_DATES
(
fileNumber in number
, firstName in varchar2
, lastName in varchar2
, firstAppointmentDateKey in number
, lastAppointmentDateKey in number
) as

/*
*/
begin

-- Write the account record
insert into account (start_date_key, end_date_key, file_number, last_name, first_name)
values (firstAppointmentDateKey, lastAppointmentDateKey, fileNumber, lastName, firstName);

end create_account_with_dates;
